<plot>Funny thing about Daisy is that she names her passwords after men she fantasizes about. Then her husband Dave discovers that she's named one after a guy she actually knows. Well, not exactly a guy. More of a two-way home alarm system manned by a perfect gentleman. Anthony is suave, passionate, and knows exactly what Daisy likes. He knows how to turn Daisy on. Now Dave has to turn him off.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?425565</url></doc>
